reviews.text: Place with a great lunch and dinner menu + a good ambiance.
Good food for a moda rate price

Hey what’s up food hunters 😎? Wanna eat like a Hongkie(local people)? i went in this place for lunch , we have order two lunch set Spanish style roast chicken and a beef tongue kebabs they both comes with a soup and a drink , they put some herbs to roast the spanish chicken and the chicken meat is juice taste good and the beef tongue is little bit over cook but still yummy , i have to say the beef soup that comes with the set is so good its so home made , the there is no queue when i get here at 13:00 on weekdays , i spend about HK$160 for the lunch , Overall - clean & neat ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , food quality ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , atmosphere ⭐️⭐️out of 5 , pricing ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , if u like my review please hit that LIKE ❤️button thanks and i will see u guys on the next one , love n peace ✌🏻-Detour Guide-

第一次來這間餐廳, 環境氣氛座位也不錯, 當晚只看到一個服務員, 可是卻給我的感覺是態度很友善和有效率, 食物質素和美味超水準, 真的很值得推介大家來這裏聚會
